\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 And with this the words of the prophets agree, just as it is written:\uc0\u8232 
\fs16 \cf2 \up13 16
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 'After this I will return And will rebuild the tabernacle of David, which has fallen 
\f0\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl300\sa240\partightenfactor0

