\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 25
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 it seemed good to us, being assembled with one accord, to send chosen men to you with our beloved Barnabas and Paul, 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 26
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 men who have risked their lives for the name of our Lord Jesus Christ.\uc0\u8232 
\fs16 \cf2 \up13 27
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 We have therefore sent Judas and Silas, who will also report the same things by 
\f0\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl300\sa240\partightenfactor0

