\f0\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl180\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 28
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 For it seemed good to the Holy Spirit, and to us, to lay upon you no greater burden than these necessary things: 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 29
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 that you abstain from things offered to idols, from blood, from things strangled, and from sexual immorality. If you keep yourselves from these, you will do well. Farewell. 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 30
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 So when they were sent off, they came to Antioch; and when they had gathered the multitude together, they delivered the letter. 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 31
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 When they had read it, they rejoiced over its encouragement.\uc0\u8232 
\fs16 \cf2 \up13 32
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 Now Judas and Silas, themselves being prophets also, exhorted and strengthened 
\f0\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl300\sa240\partightenfactor0

