\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 7
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 After they had come to Mysia, they tried to go into Bithynia, but the Spirit did not permit them. 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 8
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 So passing by Mysia, they came down to Troas.\uc0\u8232 
\fs16 \cf2 \up13 9
