\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 10
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 Now after he had seen the vision, immediately we sought to go to Macedonia, concluding that the Lord had called us to preach the gospel to them. 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 11
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 Therefore, sailing from Troas, we ran a straight course to Samothrace, and the next day came to Neapolis, 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 12
