\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 22
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 Then the multitude rose up together against them; and the magistrates tore off their clothes and commanded them to be beaten with rods. 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 23
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 And when they had laid many stripes on them, they threw them into prison, commanding the jailer to keep them securely. 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 24
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 Having received such a charge, he put them into the inner prison and fastened their feet in the stocks. 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 25
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 But at midnight Paul and Silas were praying and singing hymns to God, and the prisoners were listening to them. 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 26
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 Suddenly there was a great earthquake, so that the foundations of the prison were shaken; and immediately all the doors were opened and everyone's chains were loosed. 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 27
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 And the keeper of the prison, awaking from sleep and seeing the prison doors open, supposing the prisoners had fled, drew his sword and was about to kill himself. 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 28
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 But Paul called with a loud voice, saying, "Do yourself no harm, for we are all here." 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 29
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 Then he called for a light, ran in, and fell down trembling before Paul and Silas. 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 30
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 And he brought them out and said, "Sirs, what must I do to be saved?" 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 31
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 So they said, "Believe on the Lord Jesus Christ, and you will be saved, you and your household." 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 32
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 Then they spoke the word of the Lord to him and to all who were in his house. 
\fs16 \cf2 \up13 33
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 And he took them the same hour of the night and washed their stripes. And 
\f0\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl300\sa240\partightenfactor0

