\f0\fs24 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl180\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 34
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 Now when he had brought them into his house, he set food before them; and he rejoiced, having believed in God with all his household. 
\f0\fs24 \

\f1\fs16 \cf2 \up13 35
\fs26\fsmilli13333 \cf3 \up0 And when it was day, the magistrates sent the officers, saying, "Let those men go." 
\fs16 \cf2 \up13 36
